{"tid":919312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張家口爆炸至少22死22傷　應急管理部工作組赴現場","createTime":"2018-11-28T02:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T04:54:28.000Z","uid":217062,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b85df2c8560161b79c8b36e27823d525c081ed84","tid":919312,"uid":217062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"河北省張家口市一間化工公司附近凌晨發生爆炸，引發大火，最少22人死亡，22人受傷。事發於橋東區河北盛華化工有限公司附近，傷者已分別送往河北北方學院第一醫院等醫院救治。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段看到，事發時現場火光熊熊，內地傳媒報道，距離現場2.6公里的居民都聽到相信是爆炸造成的巨響，在睡夢中驚醒。事故導致38輛大貨車和12部車輛焚燒，網上圖片見到，附近大批車輛已燒剩支架。當局在現場搜救及調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸地點附近的盛華化工公司的工作人員聲稱，爆炸並非發生在公司之內，而是在附近的馬路，公司員工都正常上班，但公司已經暫時停產。<br />\n<br />\n應急管理部派出副部長付建華率領工作組前往現場，協助善後及調查等工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1430541-20181128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1430541-20181128.htm&d=uNoWp92JVkE6MadDRBf1OPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5d519fb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1430541-20181128.htm&h=555b5f2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1430541-20181128.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n睇錯咗[口爆]<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ee9d46f8ed4faae1fc88f33cea88e72a4d9a1a","tid":919312,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:57:13.000Z","msg":"到現場發現只是小孩放煙花"},{"pid":"93a8ca8e7a762ed18ed1f580a6a23cd93ddc0edb","tid":919312,"uid":32308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"睇到張家輝口爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1a75f7d909344a21fe82d2ed8db0c959eb5d88","tid":919312,"uid":217062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a8ca8e7a762ed18ed1f580a6a23cd93ddc0edb","tid":919312,"uid":32308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"睇到張家輝口爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96f5cd6baf7339668b82a77c99cc9f03322cb61","tid":919312,"uid":89857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"i say ya yi ye"},{"pid":"509fde4849eb8dac310dc2745edefa69b2426a99","tid":919312,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"我俾碌蕉你含"},{"pid":"bf0da33ebcd43775923f6ef8434889360733c84e","tid":919312,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"口爆至少死幾億喎... <br />\n<br />\n張家真係要去睇醫生"},{"pid":"db8c817c8d1981aee73e69fa83c089b6b81d6d1d","tid":919312,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"應急管理部定係維穩部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716f268c91e07cbc16983379d6b0d98ece81cf10","tid":919312,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6074a84c74543e16d56b1c613b9c9799b8cdcb8","tid":919312,"uid":217062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T04:54:28.000Z","msg":"所以標點符號好重要<br />\n<br />\n張家，口爆，炸至少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}